These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, folk, ambient, blues
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hedgehog, horse, goldfish
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the fan of punk is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the fan of blues is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | blues | ambient | folk | punk   |
| Pet   | hedgehog  | turtle     | horse   | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, snowmobile, boat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, soul, funk, ambient
1. the person driving the boat is the fan of soul##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | boat | jet-ski | tram    |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | soul      | d&b | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, mah-jongg, poker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, techno, country, rock
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the person playing domino is the fan of soul##1
3. the fan of techno is on the far right##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Game         | domino | poker | mah-jongg   | billiard |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | country | rock | techno         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, fishing, chess, rock-climbing
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, poker, bridge
1. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person playing go is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | fishing | drawing  | chess      |
| Game         | backgammon | bridge   | poker | go |

