.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, scooter, snowmobile
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, british, french, mexican
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the french is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the british is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | scooter | train | skateboard |
| Nationality    | indonesian       | mexican | french | british     |

