.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
House: futuristic, farmhouse, tower, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, may, august
1. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the tower house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| House   | gothic-revival | tower | futuristic | farmhouse |
| Birthday           | june      | may | august | february    |

