.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, ice-hockey, basketball
House: townhouse, cottage, futuristic, colonial
1. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | skateboarding | climbing | basketball  |
| House           | futuristic | townhouse | colonial       | cottage |

