.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, sunflower, begonia
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, almond-milk, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Flower         | sunflower | tulip      | amaryllis | begonia |
| Beverage   | 7up          | sprite | almond-milk     | juice    |

