2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | april    | december       | may | august   |
| Hobby     | video-games | gardening | reading   | drawing |

