.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, fish, ferret
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, russian, indonesian, japanese
1. the australian is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the japanese is on the left of the indonesian##1
4. the russian is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Pet    | goat | fish  | hedgehog | ferret |
| Nationality   | japanese | indonesian | russian          | australian    |

