.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra, tiparillo, bluemaster
House: modern, colonial, cape-cod, palace
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Cigar      | tiparillo | alhambra  | game | bluemaster |
| House   | modern  | cape-cod | palace           | colonial   |

