.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
City: miami, hamburg, san-francisco, marseilles
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, billiard, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| City   | hamburg | miami | marseilles | san-francisco  |
| Game           | chess | backgammon      | billiard | domino |

