3. the person traveling to hamburg is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
