.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, board-games, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, entrepreneur, engineer, dressmaker
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the entrepreneur##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the engineer##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the engineer##1
5. the engineer is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks | board-games  | dancing  | puzzles |
| Job   | entrepreneur   | software-developer | engineer | dressmaker   |

