4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, hamster, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | western     | crime | epic |
| Pet         | goldfish | horse | hedgehog   | hamster   |

