.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, tomato, lime, kiwi
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, card-games, gardening, board-games
1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Food           | pineapple | kiwi    | tomato    | lime |
| Hobby   | card-games      | gardening | collecting | board-games       |

