.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, monopoly, poker
There 4 different types of food: pepper, peach, eggplant, cauliflower
1. the person eating cauliflower is the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating peach##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | whist      | monopoly | poker | mah-jongg |
| Food     | pepper | cauliflower    | eggplant  | peach |

