.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, mango, zucchini, broccoli
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, may, october
1. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food      | avocado   | broccoli | mango   | zucchini      |
| Birthday   | february | october      | march | may |

