.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, water-polo, climbing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, tea, water
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | water-polo | climbing | biathlon |
| Beverage   | water     | tea    | almond-milk      | cola   |

