.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, october, february
City: hannover, marseilles, san-francisco, hamburg
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | april | october | september | february   |
| City     | san-francisco  | hannover    | marseilles       | hamburg |

 